WITH HIS GIRLFRIEND.

00:38.160 --> 00:41.370
I WASN'T IN LOVE WITH HER.
SHE WAS JUST VERY...

00:41.410 --> 00:44.920
VERY ATTRACTIVE. CLYDE AND I,
WE HAD THIS KIND OF

00:44.960 --> 00:46.500
FIGHT-ON-SIGHT CLAUSE.

00:49.250 --> 00:51.300
-"WHIPLASH"?
-NUMBER ONE FRAUD CLAIM.

00:51.340 --> 00:54.220
