HE WAS MR. ATHLETE.
HE GOT ALL THE GIRLS.

00:57.260 --> 01:00.640
YEAH, WELL, THAT WAS THEN.
NOW HIS FINANCES
ARE IN THE TOILET,

01:00.680 --> 01:02.480
