THROUGH A ROUGH TIME.

01:02.520 --> 01:04.140
IS HE STILL WITH JESSICA?

01:04.190 --> 01:06.100
AS FAR AS I KNOW. VULTURE.

01:06.150 --> 01:08.650
I'M NOT A VULTURE, DAD.
SHE'S JUST SUPER HOT.

01:08.690 --> 01:10.280
