WHIPLASH ISN'T HINDERING IT.

01:30.170 --> 01:31.170
ARE YOU SEEING THIS?

01:32.960 --> 01:34.300
UH, DAD...

01:37.180 --> 01:38.220
CLYDE!

01:45.310 --> 01:47.060
