02:28.350 --> 02:29.900
YOU HAD AN ACCIDENT, CLYDE.

02:29.940 --> 02:31.650
OH, WAIT A MINUTE,
WAIT A MINUTE!

02:33.440 --> 02:34.860
HEY, DIDN'T I GO TO
HIGH SCHOOL WITH YOU?

