MY FATHER, MALACHY.

02:45.540 --> 02:47.830
CLYDE, WERE YOU TRYING
TO KILL YOURSELF?

02:47.870 --> 02:51.210
&lt;CHUCKLES&gt; WHAT? NO. NO, NO.
KILL MYSELF, NO.

02:52.380 --> 02:54.090
SUICIDE.

02:54.130 --> 02:55.920
&lt;GRUNTS&gt; SUICIDE...

02:56.970 --> 02:59.220
THAT'S JUST,
THAT'S NOT ME, SO...

02:59.260 --> 03:00.390
EASY THERE. EASY.

03:00.430 --> 03:01.260
THE DOCTOR TELLS US
YOU'RE FINE,

03:01.300 --> 03:02.350
BUT YOU NEED TO REST.

03:03.260 --> 03:04.560
WHO ASKED YOU, ANYWAYS?

03:06.520 --> 03:07.930
I'M FINE, SO...

03:09.140 --> 03:11.060
YOU GUYS CAN JUST

03:11.100 --> 03:12.110
GO AWAY NOW.

03:15.070 --> 03:17.610
HEY, SON, HOLD UP.

03:17.650 --> 03:19.200
IF YOU WERE TRYING
TO KILL YOURSELF,

03:19.240 --> 03:21.410
WE COULD HAVE YOU
TAKEN INTO CUSTODY, SO, UH,

03:21.450 --> 03:22.910
WHY DON'T YOU JUST TELL US
WHAT'S GOING ON?

03:22.950 --> 03:24.330
&lt;GROANING&gt;

03:26.330 --> 03:28.040
OKAY, LOOK, JAKE,

03:28.080 --> 03:31.710
SINCE HIGH SCHOOL I HAVEN'T
EXACTLY BEEN CARRYING ON
AS THE GUY I WAS.

03:31.750 --> 03:33.380
REALLY, I HADN'T NOTICED?

03:33.920 --> 03:35.170
I AM A WINNER.

03:35.800 --> 03:37.380
I HAD A GOOD JOB,

03:37.420 --> 03:39.590
A HOUSE, A MARRIAGE,

03:39.630 --> 03:41.010
THEN A FEW MONTHS AGO

03:41.050 --> 03:42.760
EVERYTHING WENT
A LITTLE SNAKY.

03:42.800 --> 03:44.600
-OH, YEAH?
-[CLYDE] I LOST MY JOB,

03:44.640 --> 03:46.310
COULDN'T FIND WORK.

03:46.350 --> 03:48.430
IT WAS LIKE AFTER SPENDING
MY WHOLE LIFE ON TOP,

03:48.470 --> 03:50.390
SUDDENLY I WAS CURSED.

03:50.440 --> 03:51.640
[JAKE] WELL, YOU KNOW,
YOU STILL HAVE,

03:51.690 --> 03:53.730
YOU STILL HAVE
JESSICA, RIGHT?

03:53.770 --> 03:54.900
THAT'S TRUE.

03:54.940 --> 03:57.400
SHE WAS LIKE THE HOTTEST
THING IN HIGH SCHOOL...

03:58.860 --> 04:01.740
WHY AM I STILL LISTED
AS YOUR NEXT OF KIN?

04:01.780 --> 04:03.490
WE'RE DIVORCED, REMEMBER?

04:03.530 --> 04:05.160
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?
DIVORCED?

04:05.830 --> 04:07.330
NOT YET, WE'RE NOT.

04:07.370 --> 04:10.460
WELL, WE WILL
BE SOON. TRUST ME.

04:10.500 --> 04:13.330
HI, JESSICA, HOW YA DOING?
REMEMBER ME?

04:13.370 --> 04:15.670
JAKE DOYLE, FROM HIGH SCHOOL?

04:15.710 --> 04:17.380
JESS, I TOLD YOU
NOT TO TALK TO HIM

04:17.420 --> 04:18.420
UNTIL AFTER
THE SETTLEMENT.

04:18.460 --> 04:20.880
YEAH, I KNOW, WALLY.
JUST GIVE US A SECOND.

04:23.550 --> 04:25.260
-&lt;WALTER STUTTERS&gt;
-WALLY?

04:25.300 --> 04:26.390
I'M REPPING HER
IN THE DIVORCE.

04:26.430 --> 04:27.430
SHE'S AN OLD FRIEND.

04:28.560 --> 04:29.470
