24:12.700 --> 24:15.580
ANYWAYS, WE GOT TO
TRACK DOWN CLYDE,

24:15.620 --> 24:18.370
AND I THINK WE SHOULD
TAKE ON CHILI. I MEAN,

24:18.410 --> 24:19.580
HE CAN'T BE THAT BAD, RIGHT?

24:19.620 --> 24:21.750
-TELL THAT TO YOUR BACK.
