AND WHY'D YOU MAKE HIM
STAB ME THREE TIMES?

24:25.670 --> 24:28.050
I WAS PLAYING THE PART, DES.
GET OVER YOURSELF.

24:30.880 --> 24:32.880
RIGHT. OKAY, SO

24:32.930 --> 24:35.680
ACCORDING TO THE FILE
TINNY SNAGGED FOR US,

24:35.720 --> 24:39.520
JESSICA HAD A DEPOSIT OF
10 G'S TO HER BANK ACCOUNT
THE SAME DAY

24:39.560 --> 24:41.600
THAT CLYDE'S 100 WENT MISSING.

24:41.640 --> 24:43.520
IS THAT SO?

24:43.560 --> 24:46.110
OKAY, MALACHY, ME AND YOU,
WE'RE GOING TO
GO FIND CHILI POWDER.

24:46.150 --> 24:47.980
CHILI... PO... CHILI, CHILI...

24:48.020 --> 24:49.860
