I SHOULD GO TALK TO JESSICA...

25:04.330 --> 25:05.960
ALONE. &lt;CLEARS THROAT&gt;

25:14.300 --> 25:16.550
-CAN I HELP YOU?
-OH, I SEE
YOU SOLD YOUR HOUSE.

25:16.590 --> 25:20.310
YEAH. OH, THE BANK,
THEY MADE US AN AMAZING OFFER.

25:20.350 --> 25:22.310
-IS THAT RIGHT?
-MMM-HMM.

25:22.350 --> 25:24.140
A LOT OF YOUR NEIGHBORS
HAVE SOLD TOO.

25:24.190 --> 25:27.980
YEAH, YOU KNOW THAT BANK GUY,
UH, JEFF VALLIS, SOMETHING.

25:28.020 --> 25:29.690
HE MADE US ALL HUGE OFFERS.

25:30.690 --> 25:31.570
HARD TO SAY NO.

25:32.820 --> 25:33.740
APPARENTLY.

25:45.750 --> 25:46.710
[MAL] CHILI?

25:48.670 --> 25:49.670
&lt;DINGS&gt;

25:54.130 --> 25:55.590
GREET ALL YOUR
CUSTOMERS LIKE THIS?

25:56.890 --> 25:59.010
ONLY THE ONES I LIKE.

25:59.050 --> 26:00.640
I DON'T SUPPOSE
YOU GOT MY MONEY.

26:00.680 --> 26:02.560
NOPE.

26:02.600 --> 26:06.020
YOU USED TO BE A COP, HUH?
I RECALL BEING BUSTED
BY YOU A FEW YEARS BACK.

26:06.060 --> 26:08.770
-GOOD FOR YOU.
WHERE'S CLYDE?
-DEAD.

26:09.650 --> 26:11.270
IF YOU DON'T GET MY MONEY.

26:12.860 --> 26:14.990
WELL, I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

26:15.030 --> 26:17.820
