HE'S STILL ALIVE FIRST.

26:34.840 --> 26:36.880
DID YOU DO THIS? HUH?

26:36.930 --> 26:37.930
&lt;GRUNTS&gt;

26:43.770 --> 26:46.310
I ONLY HALF HIT YOU,
SO CONSIDER
YOURSELF LUCKY!

26:47.770 --> 26:48.810
CLYDE!

26:50.690 --> 26:51.860
CLYDE!

26:58.820 --> 27:00.990
UH, JESS, JESSICA?

27:01.030 --> 27:02.410
JESSICA, SORRY TO
TROUBLE YOU.

27:04.240 --> 27:06.290
