27:14.670 --> 27:16.590
SO YOU DIDN'T
FIND IT ON THE LAWN?

27:17.670 --> 27:19.970
LOOK, I KNOW THAT

27:20.010 --> 27:22.510
YOU HAD A CRUSH ON ME
YOUR WHOLE LIFE.
I GET THAT.

27:22.550 --> 27:25.520
