REMEMBER ME.

27:27.060 --> 27:29.100
I DIDN'T. BUT

27:29.140 --> 27:33.480
THEN I DID. SAME LOSER.
SAME CAR.

27:33.520 --> 27:35.610
OH, THAT'S A DIFFERENT
CAR, ACTUALLY.

27:35.650 --> 27:40.070
