IF YOU DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT CLYDE'S 100,000 BUCKS,

27:40.110 --> 27:42.820
WHERE DID YOU GET
THE 10 GRAND
THAT YOU DEPOSITED

27:42.870 --> 27:46.700
INTO YOUR BANK ACCOUNT
THE DAY THAT CLYDE'S
MONEY WENT MISSING?

27:46.740 --> 27:51.540
