MONEY FROM ANYONE
IS NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

27:56.300 --> 27:57.840
-CREEP.
-&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;

28:02.760 --> 28:04.550
YEAH?

28:04.600 --> 28:06.100
I'M GOING TO KILL VALLIS.

28:06.140 --> 28:07.810
