HE'S BANGING JESSICA

28:07.850 --> 28:10.190
AND HE HAS MY 100 G'S.

28:10.230 --> 28:12.900
-CLYDE, WHERE ARE YOU?
-I'M AT THE BANK.

28:12.940 --> 28:14.900
I'M GOING TO KILL HIM,
IF IT KILLS ME, JAKE.

28:15.610 --> 28:18.150
-YEAH.
-JU... HOLD ON.

28:23.780 --> 28:26.030
-JEFF VALLIS!
-[WOMAN] WHAT THE HELL?

28:26.080 --> 28:27.740
-CLYDE, WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?
-TAKING IT...

28:27.790 --> 28:29.410
-[WOMAN] OH, MY GOD!
-JAKE,

28:29.450 --> 28:32.370
THIS HAS GOT TO BE DONE.
I'M GOING TO WIN THIS.

28:32.420 --> 28:34.630
JAKE, I AM A WINNER
AND I'M GOING TO WIN THIS!

28:34.670 --> 28:35.880
[WOMAN] OH, MY GOD!

28:35.920 --> 28:37.800
-&lt;SCREAMING&gt;
-JEFF VALLIS!
I'M CALLING YOU OUT!

28:38.380 --> 28:39.800
&lt;PEOPLE GASP&gt;

28:40.880 --> 28:42.590
HOLD ON. HOLD ON, OKAY?

28:42.630 --> 28:45.680
I DON'T WANT SOME
TRIGGER HAPPY MALL COP
TO KILL THE GUY!

28:45.720 --> 28:46.930
CLYDE?

28:47.680 --> 28:49.560
MY WIFE...

28:49.600 --> 28:50.850
-CLYDE.
-[CLYDE] YOU WERE...

28:53.440 --> 28:54.730
CLYDE.

28:54.770 --> 28:56.020
&lt;SNORING&gt;

28:56.810 --> 28:57.860
CLYDE?

28:58.940 --> 29:00.740
-CLYDE? WAKE UP, CLYDE!
-&lt;SNORING&gt;

29:00.780 --> 29:02.820
