EVERYONE JUST STAY CALM.

29:17.290 --> 29:19.630
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
I DON'T WANT YOUR WALLETS.

29:19.670 --> 29:22.220
I DON'T WANT... STOP IT!
STOP GIVING ME YOUR WALLETS!

29:22.260 --> 29:23.550
THIS IS NOT A ROBBERY.

29:23.590 --> 29:26.390
EVERYONE, THIS IS
NOT A ROBBERY!

29:26.430 --> 29:28.890
