-[MAN] OH, MY GOD,
HE'S A TERRORIST!

29:28.930 --> 29:31.310
NO, NO, NO. NO, NO, NO.
I AM NOT A TERRORIST.

29:31.350 --> 29:32.980
I AM NOT A TERRORIST.

29:34.850 --> 29:36.310
&lt;SHOUTING&gt;

29:39.860 --> 29:40.860
&lt;INAUDIBLE&gt;

29:41.530 --> 29:42.900
BANK JOB, HUH?

29:45.950 --> 29:48.870
HEY, DES?
HEY, SWEETHEART, YOU OKAY?

29:49.330 --> 29:50.740
I WAS ASLEEP.

29:52.120 --> 29:54.500
WHERE AM I?
I'M IN A DIFFERENT ROOM.

29:54.540 --> 29:57.000
AM I BECOMING LIKE HIM?
LIKE CLYDE?
AM I A NARCOLEPTIC?

29:57.040 --> 30:00.000
NO, NO, SWEETHEART.
IT'S JUST THE ADRENALINE FROM
THE ALLERGY PEN WEARING OFF.

30:00.040 --> 30:01.750
I MEAN, HE DIDN'T
BITE ME, DID HE?

30:01.800 --> 30:03.670
-&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;
-CAN YOU CATCH NARCOLEPSY
IF YOU GET BIT BY ONE?

30:03.720 --> 30:05.220
OH. JUST A SEC.

30:05.260 --> 30:07.300
HEY, MAL. WHAT? WHAT?

30:07.970 --> 30:09.220
JAKE WHAT?

30:10.560 --> 30:12.470
I GOT TO GO, HUN.
TAKE CARE. BYE.

30:12.520 --> 30:13.520
OKAY.

30:16.520 --> 30:18.900
WHAT'S WITH YOU, SPAZ?
GET UP.

30:24.360 --> 30:26.780
YOU'RE ACTING SUPER WEIRD.
I CAN TELL.

30:26.820 --> 30:29.280
-AND I KNOW YOU HATE CHANDRA.
-OKAY, I HATE CHANDRA

30:29.320 --> 30:30.870
BECAUSE SHE'S
A SNOBBY LITTLE JERK.

30:30.910 --> 30:32.080
IT HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH YOU.

30:32.120 --> 30:33.540
WELL, I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU
WANT FROM ME HERE.

30:33.580 --> 30:36.920
IT'S LIKE THE MINUTE
I DON'T SHOW ANY INTEREST,

30:36.960 --> 30:38.210
YOU'RE ALL OVER ME.
AND THEN THE NEXT MINUTE,

30:38.250 --> 30:40.290
WHEN I ACTUALLY SHOW
YOU SOME ATTENTION,
YOU TREAT ME LIKE...

30:40.340 --> 30:42.210
-DES!
-WHAT? IT'S TRUE!

30:42.250 --> 30:43.420
SHUT UP.

30:46.130 --> 30:47.130
IS JAKE ROBBING A BANK?

30:49.010 --> 30:50.850
-HI.
-HI.

30:52.140 --> 30:55.350
-DES, ARE YOU OKAY?
-YES, I'M FINE. YES.

30:55.810 --> 30:57.480
YES.

30:57.520 --> 31:00.650
PUT YOUR HANDS DOWN!
PUT YOUR HANDS DOWN, NOW.

31:00.690 --> 31:02.980
OKAY? EVERYONE JUST
RELAX AND BREATHE.

31:03.020 --> 31:04.480
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

31:04.530 --> 31:06.400
PUT THE MONEY BACK
OUT OF YOUR PURSE, OKAY?

31:06.440 --> 31:09.240
NOBODY STEAL ANYTHING.
WE'RE NOT ROBBING ANYTHING,

31:09.280 --> 31:11.070
OKAY? PUT IT AWAY.

31:11.120 --> 31:12.870
THIS IS ALL

31:13.830 --> 31:16.120
A HORRIBLE

31:16.160 --> 31:17.710
MISUNDERSTANDING.

31:17.750 --> 31:21.750
ALL RIGHT, NOW WE'RE
JUST GOING TO RELAX HERE,
ALL RIGHT? UM...

31:21.790 --> 31:24.880
WHAT WE'RE GOING TO DO IS,
IN A FEW MINUTES,
WE'LL ALL JUST GO HOME,

31:24.920 --> 31:27.010
PRETEND THIS NEVER HAPPENED,

31:27.050 --> 31:29.680
AND, UH, NO HARM AND, UH...

31:30.050 --> 31:31.470
AND NO FOUL.

31:31.510 --> 31:33.600
[LESLIE] JAKE DOYLE,
WE HAVE YOU SURROUNDED.

31:33.640 --> 31:35.350
COME OUT
WITH YOUR HANDS UP!

31:35.390 --> 31:36.850
OH, CRAP.

31:36.890 --> 31:38.690
[MAL] HOW'D THIS HAPPEN?
[ROSE] I HAVE NO CLUE.

31:38.730 --> 31:39.980
HEY, LESLIE,

31:40.020 --> 31:41.770
ANY IDEA WHAT HE'S
DOING IN THERE?

31:41.810 --> 31:43.020
HE'S ROBBING A BANK.

31:43.060 --> 31:44.650
OH, DEAR LORD.

31:44.690 --> 31:46.610
[JAKE] I GOT TO THINK HERE,
I GOT TO THINK. SO, UH...

31:46.650 --> 31:50.820
EVERYONE GET UP AND, UH,
GO OVER THERE TO WHERE
THE GUARD IS TO, RIGHT THERE.

31:50.860 --> 31:52.910
YOU SAID YOU WEREN'T ROBBING
THE PLACE, RIGHT, SO, SO...

31:52.950 --> 31:55.160
I'M NOT ROBBING THE PLACE,
BUT I STILL WANT YOU
TO DO WHAT I SAY.

31:55.200 --> 31:57.580
SO GO, GO, GO. GO, GO, GO!
EVERYONE, KEEP GOING.

31:57.620 --> 31:59.120
KEEP GOING STRAIGHT, STRAIGHT,
STRAIGHT. THERE YOU GO.

31:59.160 --> 32:00.540
GET OVER THERE, EVERYONE.

32:00.580 --> 32:03.130
JAKE, ARE YOU
ROBBING THE PLACE?

32:03.170 --> 32:05.210
-ARE YOU
OUT OF YOUR MIND?
-OH, WELCOME BACK!

32:06.130 --> 32:07.760
DIPSHIT.

32:07.800 --> 32:10.090
-VALLIS?
-YEAH. YEAH.

32:10.130 --> 32:13.590
-YOU SON OF A BITCH!
-YOU! STAY!

32:15.100 --> 32:16.010
STAY.

32:18.220 --> 32:20.980
OKAY, VALLIS. SIT.

32:21.020 --> 32:24.230
ALTHOUGH CLYDE HERE
IS THE SOLE REASON
I AM IN THIS PREDICAMENT,

32:24.270 --> 32:26.150
I AM STILL
GOING TO BLAME YOU

32:26.190 --> 32:27.730
AND I'M GOING
TO SHOOT YOU

32:27.780 --> 32:30.030
IF YOU DON'T ANSWER
MY QUESTIONS DIRECTLY.

32:30.070 --> 32:31.650
-DO YOU UNDERSTAND?
-YES.

32:31.700 --> 32:34.410
OKAY. CLYDE THINKS THAT
YOU'RE SCREWING HIM OVER

32:34.450 --> 32:36.410
AND THERE ARE CURRENTLY
THREE CHARGES AGAINST YOU.

32:36.450 --> 32:39.200
NUMBER ONE.
HE THINKS THAT YOU'RE SLEEPING
WITH HIS WIFE, JESSICA.

32:39.250 --> 32:41.250
WHAT? NO.
THAT, THAT'S INSANE.

32:41.290 --> 32:43.170
I KNOW.
I TOTALLY AGREE WITH YOU,

32:43.210 --> 32:45.330
BECAUSE PERSONALLY
I REALLY DON'T THINK

32:45.380 --> 32:47.630
THAT YOU'RE HER TYPE.
I MEAN, THE HAIR COLOR,

32:47.670 --> 32:49.170
THE WAY YOU DRESS,
IT'S ALL WRONG.

32:50.090 --> 32:51.760
ANYWAY, CHARGE NUMBER TWO.

32:51.800 --> 32:54.930
HE THINKS THAT YOU STOLE
$100,000 FROM HIM.

32:54.970 --> 32:57.430
LOOKING AT YOU,
I REALLY DON'T THINK
YOU'RE THAT STUPID.

32:57.470 --> 32:59.390
I DIDN'T ROB
ANY 100 GRAND, NO.

32:59.430 --> 33:02.140
THAT BRINGS US TO
CHARGE NUMBER THREE.

33:03.770 --> 33:06.190
THAT YOU FORECLOSED
ON HIS HOUSE EARLY

33:06.230 --> 33:08.110
AND WITHOUT JUST CAUSE.

33:10.400 --> 33:11.690
RIGHT.

33:12.860 --> 33:15.070
NOW THE QUESTION I HAVE
FOR YOU, MR. VALLIS,

33:16.820 --> 33:17.990
IS WHY?

33:19.080 --> 33:21.370
-&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;
-&lt;PEOPLE GASP&gt;

33:21.410 --> 33:23.460
RELAX, EVERYONE.
IT'S A PHONE. OKAY?

33:23.500 --> 33:25.710
-JUST...
-&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;

33:27.750 --> 33:29.300
STAY AWAKE.

33:29.340 --> 33:31.550
-HELLO?
-HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND?

33:31.590 --> 33:33.010
WHY ARE YOU ROBBING A BANK?

33:33.050 --> 33:34.300
[JAKE] I AM NOT
ROBBING A BANK.

33:34.340 --> 33:35.840
IT SURE LOOKS
THAT WAY TO ME.

33:35.880 --> 33:38.510
YEAH, I KNOW IT LOOKS
THAT WAY, DAD.
THANKS... THANKS FOR THE

33:38.550 --> 33:41.560
BRILLIANT INSIGHT. OKAY?
YOU JUST KEEP EVERYONE
OUT THERE CALM,

33:41.600 --> 33:43.180
AND DON'T LEAVE
UNTIL YOU HEAR FROM ME.

33:44.520 --> 33:45.520
ANY LUCK?

33:46.440 --> 33:48.110
HE HUNG UP!

33:48.150 --> 33:49.690
-HE WHAT?
-&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;

33:50.480 --> 33:52.110
YEAH? THIS IS MALACHY.

33:52.150 --> 33:54.150
TELL YOUR BANK ROBBING SON
TO GET ME MY MONEY,

33:54.200 --> 33:57.030
OR CLYDE'S WIFE AND HER
WINNING ATTITUDE ARE TOAST.

33:59.620 --> 34:01.120
YEAH, WHOEVER THIS IS,

34:01.160 --> 34:03.790
TELL CLYDE TO GIVE
THIS GUY HIS MONEY.

34:03.830 --> 34:04.960
&lt;SNAPPING FINGERS&gt;

34:07.290 --> 34:08.290
YOU HAVE ONE HOUR.

34:12.090 --> 34:13.710
&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;

34:13.760 --> 34:16.300
[LESLIE] JAKE!
ANSWER THE PHONE!

34:16.340 --> 34:18.930
ALL RIGHT, CLYDE,
LET'S JUST GET THIS ALL
OVER WITH, OKAY?

34:18.970 --> 34:21.310
WE KNOW
THAT YOU FORECLOSED
ON CLYDE TOO EARLY

34:21.350 --> 34:24.430
AND YOU BOUGHT EVERY HOUSE
ON THE STREET
FOR OVER MARKET VALUE.

34:24.480 --> 34:25.850
WHAT ARE YOU COOKING UP

34:25.890 --> 34:27.850
AND HOW IS
JESSICA INVOLVED?

34:27.900 --> 34:30.400
OKAY, LOOK, LOOK,
I DID NOT SLEEP WITH HER.

34:30.440 --> 34:31.770
NO, NO. I JUST, UH...

34:31.820 --> 34:35.110
I, UH, PAID HER
A FEW BUCKS TO HELP ME.

34:35.150 --> 34:36.740
HELP YOU DO WHAT?

34:36.780 --> 34:38.280
I WAS USING MY POSITION
HERE AT THE BANK.

34:38.320 --> 34:40.280
I WAS BUYING UP ALL THE LAND.
I HAD A DEAL WITH HIS, UH,

34:40.320 --> 34:41.780
HIS WIFE. IF...

34:41.830 --> 34:44.290
IF SHE WAS ABLE TO
GET HIM, ALL RIGHT,
TO MISS THE PAYMENTS,

34:44.330 --> 34:48.540
I'D FORECLOSE AND, UH...

34:48.580 --> 34:50.080
I'D GIVE HER A PERCENTAGE.

34:51.540 --> 34:52.960
&lt;PEOPLE MURMURING&gt;

34:53.000 --> 34:54.460
PERCENTAGE OF WHAT?
PERCENTAGE OF WHAT?

34:54.510 --> 34:57.050
THERE'S AN OIL DISCOVERY.

34:57.090 --> 34:58.800
APPARENTLY IT WAS HUGE.

34:58.840 --> 35:00.430
I CUT HER IN. WE WERE...

35:00.470 --> 35:02.140
WE WERE GOING TO GET RICH.
THAT'S IT.

35:03.100 --> 35:04.220
SHE SOLD ME OUT.

35:06.230 --> 35:07.480
JESSICA.

35:07.520 --> 35:08.940
&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;

35:09.440 --> 35:11.770
&lt;CELL PHONE RINGING&gt;

35:15.030 --> 35:17.200
YEAH? UH, DAD, I AM, UH...

35:17.240 --> 35:19.030
WHAT YOU'D CALL KIND OF BUSY,
SO WHAT IS IT?

35:19.070 --> 35:20.360
THE LOAN SHARK'S
GOT JESSICA.

35:20.410 --> 35:21.570
[JAKE] ALL RIGHT.

35:21.620 --> 35:23.990
-YOU WAIT FOR MY SIGNAL.
-&lt;PHONE RINGING&gt;

35:24.040 --> 35:27.210
[LESLIE] ANSWER THE PHONE OR
I'LL GET THE SNIPERS SHOOTING.

35:27.250 --> 35:29.830
-TRY ME!
-OKAY, OKAY! HOLD ON!

35:31.630 --> 35:33.460
-HI THERE.
-[LESLIE] JAKE!

35:33.500 --> 35:37.050
LOOK, I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT THE WAY THIS IS
ALL PLAYING OUT

35:37.090 --> 35:39.260
IS NOT AT ALL
HOW IT'S ACTUALLY

35:39.760 --> 35:40.840
PLAYING OUT.

35:40.890 --> 35:42.350
GET THE HELL
OUT HERE NOW.

35:42.390 --> 35:44.260
OKAY. I'LL TELL YOU
WHAT I'LL DO.

35:45.430 --> 35:46.520
I'LL RELEASE ALL OF THE...

35:46.560 --> 35:48.810
-HOSTAGES?
-[JAKE] THEY'RE NOT HOSTAGES.

35:48.850 --> 35:50.480
THEY'RE PEOPLE.

35:50.520 --> 35:52.610
BANK PEOPLE. PEOPLE IN A BANK.
AND I'M...

35:52.650 --> 35:55.110
I'M JUST GOING TO GET ALL...
I'M GOING TO RELEASE THEM.

35:55.150 --> 35:57.740
AND THEN, UH, YOU WAIT
A COUPLE OF MINUTES,
AND THEN YOU,

35:57.780 --> 35:59.280
YOU COME IN
AND YOU GET ME.

35:59.320 --> 36:01.320
AND, LESLIE, FEEL FREE
TO BE ROUGH WITH ME,

36:01.360 --> 36:03.240
BECAUSE I TELL YOU,

36:03.280 --> 36:04.330
I DESERVE IT.

36:09.290 --> 36:10.330
&lt;CLICKS TONGUE&gt;

36:12.170 --> 36:13.420
DON'T SHOOT!

36:13.460 --> 36:15.630
DON'T SHOOT!
HE'S LETTING US GO!

36:15.670 --> 36:17.760
EVERYONE JUST STAY CALM.

36:19.970 --> 36:21.510
STAY CALM!

36:22.470 --> 36:23.470
&lt;PEOPLE TALKING INDISTINCTLY&gt;

36:27.260 --> 36:28.430
-MOVE IN!
-[MAN] MOVE IN!

36:29.310 --> 36:30.980
[LESLIE] PUT THE GUN DOWN NOW!

36:31.020 --> 36:32.190
ON YOUR KNEES!

36:33.730 --> 36:35.480
-JAKE!
-&lt;MUFFLED SHOUTING&gt;

36:42.240 --> 36:44.370
-AH!
-WHERE IS HE?

36:44.410 --> 36:46.870
I JUST WANTED TO MAKE
SOME MONEY. I'M SORRY.

36:49.660 --> 36:51.830
JAKE, YOU SON OF A FRIGGER.

36:59.420 --> 37:00.840
I TRUST YOU GOT ME
MY MONEY?

37:00.880 --> 37:02.840
UM, SORT OF.

37:02.880 --> 37:04.220
SORT OF?

37:04.260 --> 37:05.930
THIS MAN
JUST ROBBED A BANK.

37:05.970 --> 37:07.810
-OKAY, LOOK, I DIDN'T...
-[CLYDE] LISTEN.

37:07.850 --> 37:10.600
NO, JUST... JUST GIVE ME
A SECOND PLEASE.

37:10.640 --> 37:14.190
JUST... JESSICA, I'M LED TO
BELIEVE THAT YOU...

37:14.230 --> 37:15.310
JESSICA...

37:16.770 --> 37:18.270
SCREWED ME OVER.

37:20.110 --> 37:21.990
DID YOU TAKE
MY 100 GRAND?

37:22.030 --> 37:24.910
YES, I SCREWED YOU OVER,
BUT I NEVER
TOOK YOUR MONEY.

37:25.570 --> 37:26.820
YOU AND VALLIS...

37:27.580 --> 37:28.950
YOU SOLD ME OUT.

37:30.490 --> 37:32.460
-WHY?
-MY FUTURE.

37:33.460 --> 37:37.420
YOU COULD NEVER GIVE ME ONE,
SO I HAD TO MAKE MY OWN.

37:38.590 --> 37:40.500
I AM SO SICK
OF THIS CRAP.

37:40.550 --> 37:43.300
YEAH, I KNOW. A LOT OF
PEOPLE ARE, OKAY? JUST WAIT.

37:43.340 --> 37:45.550
I SAW YOU ON THE TV.
YOU WERE ROBBING A BANK,

37:45.590 --> 37:46.970
NOW GIVE ME MY MONEY.

37:47.010 --> 37:49.970
OH, I'M STARTING TO
FEEL SLEEPY.

37:50.010 --> 37:51.930
HERE WE GO
WITH THE FALLING ASLEEP.

37:53.140 --> 37:54.690
&lt;SNORING&gt;

37:54.730 --> 37:56.400
OKAY, LOOK,
I DIDN'T ROB A BANK.

37:56.440 --> 37:57.810
OKAY, &lt;STUTTERS&gt;
IT'S COMPLICATED.

37:57.860 --> 37:59.900
YOU KNOW WHAT? I'M JUST
GOING TO KILL YOU GUYS.

37:59.940 --> 38:01.110
GET IT OVER WITH.

38:01.150 --> 38:02.400
AND WHEN CLYDE WAKES UP,

38:02.440 --> 38:05.030
I'M GOING
TO PLAY BASEBALL
WITH HIS KNEECAPS

38:05.070 --> 38:06.280
UNTIL HE REMEMBERS

38:06.320 --> 38:07.570
WHERE HE STASHED
MY FRIGGING MONEY.

38:07.620 --> 38:09.120
HEY, CHILI.

38:09.450 --> 38:10.580
OH!

38:14.580 --> 38:15.580
&lt;GRUNTS&gt;

38:17.040 --> 38:18.420
NICE.

38:18.460 --> 38:20.960
I SUPPOSE I'LL BE GETTING OUT
OF EVERYONE'S HAIR NOW.

38:21.000 --> 38:22.460
[JAKE] WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
CLYDE, BUDDY! CLYDE!

38:22.510 --> 38:24.420
JUST, JUST, JUST, UH...
JUST PUT THE GUN DOWN.

38:24.470 --> 38:26.470
I THINK WE'VE DONE
ALL WE CAN HERE.

38:27.680 --> 38:29.300
THERE'S NOTHING
LEFT FOR ME.

38:29.350 --> 38:31.850
CLYDE, THINK ABOUT THIS NOW.

38:31.890 --> 38:33.850
JESSICA, SHE'S NEVER
GOING TO TAKE ME BACK.

38:35.810 --> 38:39.980
-I MIGHT AS WELL JUMP.
-CLYDE, HONEY, DON'T.

38:40.020 --> 38:43.440
I'M SORRY. OKAY?
I'M SORRY ABOUT THE HOUSE,

38:43.480 --> 38:44.530
ABOUT EVERYTHING.

38:45.530 --> 38:47.530
-JUST...
-JESSICA.

38:49.200 --> 38:52.200
YOU'RE SAYING
THAT THERE'S A CHANCE?

38:53.200 --> 38:54.330
GOD, NO.

38:55.290 --> 38:56.830
BUT I NEVER MEANT
TO HURT YOU.

38:58.420 --> 39:00.880
&lt;DEEP BREATH&gt;

39:00.920 --> 39:02.670
NOW, CLYDE,
YOU GIVE ME THE GUN.

39:05.210 --> 39:06.380
GIVE ME THE GUN.

39:12.600 --> 39:13.680
OKAY.

39:15.640 --> 39:16.890
LIFE'S TOO SHORT

39:16.930 --> 39:19.270
FOR YOU
TO SPEND IT WITH SOMEONE
WHO HATES YOUR GUTS.

39:20.350 --> 39:21.400
TAKE IT FROM ME.

39:21.440 --> 39:22.820
ALL RIGHT.

39:25.480 --> 39:27.570
THANK YOU.

39:27.610 --> 39:29.660
[LESLIE] JAKE DOYLE,
WE HAVE YOU SURROUNDED!

39:29.700 --> 39:31.570
COME OUT
WITH YOUR HANDS UP!

39:34.700 --> 39:36.450
UH-OH.

39:36.500 --> 39:38.580
[FEMALE OFFICER] COME WITH ME.
[MALE OFFICER]
WATCH YOUR STEP THERE.

39:41.580 --> 39:43.590
&lt;SIGHS&gt;

39:43.630 --> 39:46.130
YOU KNOW, CLYDE, WE NEVER
DID FIND OUT WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR $100,000 AFTER...

39:48.300 --> 39:50.010
THAT FREAKING KID.

39:50.050 --> 39:51.470
BUZZING UP AND DOWN
THIS ROAD,

39:51.510 --> 39:53.100
DELIVERING HIS PAPER
ON THAT BIKE.

39:55.430 --> 39:57.270
WELL, THAT ONE
LOOKS LIKE A...

39:57.310 --> 39:59.940
LIKE A BRAND NEW
DIRT BIKE.

39:59.980 --> 40:02.610
-COME ON, JAKE.
-WHERE'RE WE GOING?

40:02.650 --> 40:04.570
-JAIL.
-I'LL SEE YOU LATER, DAD.

40:04.610 --> 40:07.110
-YEAH.
-GOOD LUCK, CLYDE.

40:07.150 --> 40:08.280
THANKS, JAKE.

40:10.360 --> 40:11.570
WATCH THIS.

40:14.620 --> 40:15.990
HEY!

40:19.500 --> 40:21.290
NICE BIKE YOU GOT THERE.

40:21.330 --> 40:22.790
WHAT DO YOU WANT
WITH MY SON?

40:22.830 --> 40:24.750
YEAH, WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

40:24.790 --> 40:27.210
DID YOU GET YOUR NEWSPAPER
THE DAY YOUR 100 G'S
WENT MISSING?

40:27.250 --> 40:29.170
NO, BUT I'M NOT
FOLLOWING YOU.

40:29.220 --> 40:30.670
SO THERE'S A CHANCE
YOUR WIFE WASN'T
THE ONLY ONE

40:30.720 --> 40:32.840
WHO SAW YOU PASSED OUT
IN FRONT OF YOUR CAR
THAT DAY?

40:32.890 --> 40:34.220
OH.

40:35.720 --> 40:36.930
YOU LITTLE SHAGGER.

40:36.970 --> 40:38.600
&lt;SIREN WAILING&gt;

40:38.640 --> 40:40.480
YOU STOLE MY MONEY,
DIDN'T YOU?

40:40.520 --> 40:42.440
MY GUESS IS WHEN YOU
FELL ASLEEP, CLYDE,

40:42.480 --> 40:43.940
THE KID WAS GRABBING HIS
PAPERS FOR THE NEXT DAY

40:43.980 --> 40:45.520
AND FOUND THE BRIEFCASE
FULL OF CASH.

40:45.560 --> 40:47.570
-&lt;GROANS&gt;
-HERE WE ARE.

40:47.610 --> 40:49.490
-WHERE'S MY MONEY?
-YOU TOLD ME
YOU WON THAT MONEY

40:49.530 --> 40:51.360
ON SCRATCH TICKETS
AT THE STORE.

40:51.400 --> 40:53.490
WHERE'S MY MONEY AND HOW
MUCH DO YOU HAVE LEFT?

40:57.910 --> 40:58.910
&lt;LAUGHS&gt;

41:04.880 --> 41:06.170
[CHANDRA] TINNY STABBED YOU?

41:06.210 --> 41:09.380
WELL, NOT PHYSICALLY, BUT
SHE INSTRUCTED SOMEONE TO.

41:09.420 --> 41:10.880
WELL, I'M GLAD YOU'RE OKAY.

41:10.920 --> 41:13.630
AND IF YOU WANT I CAN
PRESCRIBE SOME MEDICATION.

41:13.680 --> 41:15.470
OH, THAT'D BE
GREAT ACTUALLY,

41:15.510 --> 41:16.720
BUT CAN YOU MAKE SURE
THERE'S NO STEROIDS IN IT,

41:16.760 --> 41:17.810
BECAUSE I DON'T WANT TO
GET ANY BIGGER?

41:18.850 --> 41:21.060
NOT THAT KIND
OF MEDICATION.

41:21.100 --> 41:22.940
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.
ACTUALLY, UM...

41:23.690 --> 41:25.060
UM, ABOUT THAT.

41:26.810 --> 41:28.690
WHAT'S GOING ON, DES?

41:28.730 --> 41:30.610
THIS IS ABOUT TINNY, ISN'T IT?

41:30.650 --> 41:32.650
UH, NO. TINNY? NO. WE'RE...

41:33.450 --> 41:34.820
-WE'RE FRIENDS.
-REALLY?

41:35.660 --> 41:37.660
YEAH. OKAY. OKAY.

41:37.700 --> 41:40.120
THIS IS, UM, THIS IS ABOUT US.

41:40.160 --> 41:41.450
I THINK...

41:42.710 --> 41:44.080
YOU'RE REALLY PRETTY.

41:44.750 --> 41:47.290
I THINK YOU'RE REALLY FUNNY.

41:47.330 --> 41:50.630
I THINK YOU'RE REALLY SMART.
I THINK YOU'RE FUN.

41:50.670 --> 41:51.840
JUST SAY IT, DES.

41:51.880 --> 41:54.340
I DON'T THINK I'M READY TO BE
IN THIS RELATIONSHIP WITH YOU.

41:57.800 --> 42:00.680
FINE. FINE.

42:00.720 --> 42:02.390
YOU TAKE
CARE OF YOURSELF, DES.

42:07.900 --> 42:09.900
[WALTER] I THINK THIS IS
THE REAL TROUBLE, PAL.

42:09.940 --> 42:12.280
I DON'T KNOW HOW
I'M GOING TO GET YOU
OUT OF THIS.

42:12.320 --> 42:14.610
ALL FOR THAT MOPE,
CLYDE COWLEY.

42:14.650 --> 42:16.360
TALK ABOUT YOUR BAD LUCK.

42:16.410 --> 42:18.490
HEY, HOW DID IT
GO WITH JESSICA?

42:18.530 --> 42:20.240
SHE LOST INTEREST
PRETTY QUICKLY.

42:20.280 --> 42:23.160
-AH. SORRY, BUDDY.
-WE MADE OUT.

42:24.160 --> 42:25.910
FELT HER BOOB A BIT.

42:25.960 --> 42:29.750
YOU KNOW, THAT WAS MY
EXACT FANTASY ABOUT HER
IN HIGH SCHOOL.

42:35.550 --> 42:37.510
JAKE, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO TELL YOU.

42:37.550 --> 42:39.300
YOU'RE CAUGHT ON TAPE
ROBBING A BANK,

42:39.350 --> 42:40.970
MISLEADING POLICE,
EVADING POLICE,

42:41.010 --> 42:44.980
POSSESSION OF A FIREARM,
AND DON'T EVEN GET ME
STARTED ON CHILI POWER.

42:45.020 --> 42:48.310
WELL, WHEN YOU STACK
THE THINGS ALL UP AGAINST
EACH OTHER LIKE THAT,

42:48.350 --> 42:49.650
IT DOES LOOK KIND OF...

42:50.940 --> 42:52.150
YEAH.

42:52.190 --> 42:53.320
IS THERE ANYTHING
YOU WANT TO TELL ME HERE?

42:53.360 --> 42:54.820
I WOULD ADVISE YOU NOT TO.

42:56.780 --> 42:59.240
THAT'S A NICE OUTFIT.

42:59.280 --> 43:02.740
LOOK, SOMETHING TELLS ME,
HAVING WATCHED THE TAPES
OF THE BANK ROBBERY,

43:02.790 --> 43:04.700
THAT YOU WEREN'T THERE
TO STEAL ANYTHING.

43:04.750 --> 43:06.830
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE ANY
WIGGLE ROOM TO GET ME OUT.

43:07.410 --> 43:09.040
I'M SORRY.

43:09.080 --> 43:11.590
I TOLD YOU YOUR CRAP WAS
GOING TO GET YOU IN TROUBLE,

43:11.630 --> 43:12.710
AND NOW IT HAS.

43:17.760 --> 43:20.720
LOOKS LIKE YOU'RE GOING TO
BE BUNKING IN HER MAJESTY'S
PEN FOR SOME TIME.

43:25.930 --> 43:27.690
HOME SWEET HOME.

