♪ I'M NOT GONNA BE

43:41.870 --> 43:43.660
♪ A CRUCIFIX PIN CUSHION

43:43.700 --> 43:44.830
♪ I'M NOT GONNA BE

43:44.870 --> 43:46.870
♪ A VOODOO DOLL

43:46.910 --> 43:49.710
♪ I FLY WITH MILITARY PRECISION

43:49.750 --> 43:51.920
♪ THIS IS MY HOLY GROUND

43:51.960 --> 43:53.000
♪ OH, YEAH

